Lyrics:-

M-Haego...Haego... 
    Suna.. Haego..

Haego Haego tike suna
Haego Haego tike suna
Haego Haego tike suna
Haego Haego tike suna

Haego Haego Suna Tamku dekhi kari 
Haye Haye re sundiri , A Mor Sundiri
Hae go suna tumar thhane.....
RAHICHHE MOR MANA..

Antara:-
M-Gudunu Mudke go tumen sundiri ........ tumen sundiri
    Gudunu Mudke go.....Mudke go......Mudke go
    Gudunu Mudke go tumen sundiri
    Tumar kaen bali gaemi guna 
    Tume pare go tume pare 
    Tume pare mor udiyan Janhan..

F-Thau Go Thau Go babu A babu Thau 
    Ete Katha Mate Nai Kahana 
    Laaje Laaje Laaje Thari Jauchhe
    Lubh Lubhani Mor Juba Jaubana

M-Tumar Gaal ke Dekhi Kari  
    Chal ke dekhi Kari
    Haego Suna Tumar Thhane
    RAHICHHE MOR MANA


F-Eta Kaen Chalana Mor Dhana Go 
    Eta Kaen Chalana...
    Katha Pade Kahemi Baluchhen 
    Kaen je Tame Nai Sunuchha 

M- Kana Kaheba je ta Kahi Diana

F- Haego Haego Tike Suna  
     Haego Haego Tike Suna  
     Haego Haego Tike Suna  
    Haego Haego Tike Suna 

Haego Haego Suna Tamku Dekhi Kari
Haye Haye Mor Sundura
A Mor Sundura
Haego Suna Tumar Thhane
RAHICHHE MOR MANA....

snippet.title: Saraswati Mantra | Om Saraswati Namo Namah | Basant Panchami | Saraswati Puja | Master Your Mind
snippet.description:
Experience the divine power of the Saraswati Mantra, a sacred Vedic chant dedicated to Goddess Saraswatiâ€”the eternal source of wisdom, intelligence, creativity, and clarity of thought. This mantra is traditionally known to enhance learning, focus, communication skills, and decision-making abilities, which are essential foundations for achieving success in modern life, including career growth, financial planning, and wealth creation.

In todayâ€™s fast-paced world of technology, luxury lifestyle, high-performance careers, and global financial markets, mental clarity and disciplined thinking are more valuable than ever. Regular listening to the Saraswati Mantra helps calm the mind, sharpen analytical skills, and align your thoughts toward positive outcomes. A focused mind is crucial for excelling in investment strategies, stock market analysis, business leadership, entrepreneurship, and long-term financial stability.

Many successful individuals across the world believe that spiritual discipline complements material growth. When your mind is balanced, you make wiser choicesâ€”whether itâ€™s related to personal finance, wealth management, real estate investment, or building assets that support a premium lifestyle. Listening to this mantra during meditation, work, or study can support better concentration, improved productivity, and confident communicationâ€”skills valued in corporate careers, high-income professions, and global businesses.

This devotional audio is ideal for those aspiring to grow in financial wealth, career success, and intellectual excellence, while remaining spiritually grounded. It resonates strongly with audiences interested in luxury cars, automobiles, high-end brands, financial freedom, passive income, and smart money habits. A calm and intelligent mindset also supports better judgment when dealing with banking, insurance, mutual funds, cryptocurrency awareness, and international investments.

Listening to the Saraswati Mantra daily can inspire discipline, creativity, and confidenceâ€”qualities that align naturally with success in business growth, startup ecosystems, digital marketing, global employment opportunities, and lifestyle goals. Whether you are a student, professional, entrepreneur, or investor, this mantra helps cultivate inner strength that supports both spiritual peace and material progress.

ğŸŒ¸ Chant along or play during work or meditation
ğŸŒ¸ Maintain a positive intention for knowledge, growth, and prosperity

May Goddess Saraswati bless you with wisdom that leads to meaningful success, balanced wealth, and a fulfilled life

Singer, Composition, Lyrics :- Sohini mishra

snippet.title: Supergirl | Blast Off :30
snippet.description:
Itâ€™s called making an entrance. #Supergirl lands in theaters and IMAX June 26.

â€œSupergirl,â€ DC Studiosâ€™ newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El. Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa. DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther. Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, â€œSupergirl,â€ which will be in theaters and IMAXÂ® across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Sarvam Maya | JioHotstar Official Trailer | Nivin Pauly | Aju Varghese | Riya Shibu | Jan 30
snippet.description:
Presenting the JioHotstar official trailer of #SarvamMaya starring Nivin Pauly, Aju Varghese and Riya Shibu. Streaming exclusively on JioHotstar from January 30.

Nivin Pauly, Aju Varghese, Riya Shibu, Janardhanan, Preity Mukhundhan, Raghunath Paleri and Madhu Wariar

Written and Directed by Akhil Sathyan
Producer: Dr. Ajayya Kumar and Rajeev Menon
Banner: Firefly Films
Cinematography: Sharan Velayudhan
Music: Justin Prabhakaran
Editors: Akhil Sathyan, Rathin Radhakrishnan
Sync Sound / Sound Design: Anil Radhakrishnan (Bell Audio)
Production Designer: Rajeevan
Executive Producer: Biju Thomas
Costumes: Sameera Saneesh
Art Director: Aji Kuttiyani
Make up: Sajeev Saji
Action Director: Kalai Kingson
Choreography: Brinda
First AD: Aaron Mathew
Associate Director: Vandana Surya
Line Producer: Vinod Sekhar
VFX : Jishnu R Pisharady, FlyingPluto Studios, Hanosh Madhavan,  Arundas K H
Stills: Rohith K S
Poster Design: Aesthetic Kunjamma
Promotions : Snakeplant LLP (PRO: Hains)

Ratha Saptami is the highly auspicious day when Lord Surya (The Sun God) enlightened the whole world with his warmth and light. It is traditionally celebrated as the birthday of Lord Surya Narayana. Listening to these powerful devotional songs on this sacred day is believed to wash away sins and bless the devotee with glowing health, longevity, and success in all endeavors.

This collection features soul-stirring hymns and chants dedicated to the Sun God, perfect for your morning prayers and Ratha Saptami rituals. Let the divine rays of Surya Dev bring positivity and prosperity into your life.

Key Highlights:

Powerful Surya Ashtakam & Aditya Hrudayam

Divine Ratha Saptami Special Chants

Soulful Sun God Devotional Hits

Ideal for Morning Meditation and Worship

Ratha Saptami is the highly auspicious day when Lord Surya (The Sun God) enlightened the whole world with his warmth and light. It is traditionally celebrated as the birthday of Lord Surya Narayana. Listening to these powerful devotional songs on this sacred day is believed to wash away sins and bless the devotee with glowing health, longevity, and success in all endeavors.

This collection features soul-stirring hymns and chants dedicated to the Sun God, perfect for your morning prayers and Ratha Saptami rituals. Let the divine rays of Surya Dev bring positivity and prosperity into your life.

Key Highlights:

Powerful Surya Ashtakam & Aditya Hrudayam

Divine Ratha Saptami Special Chants

Soulful Sun God Devotional Hits

Ideal for Morning Meditation and Worship

May the blessings of Lord Surya Narayana be with you always. Like, Share, and Subscribe for more spiritual content!

id.description:

Keberuntungan saya dalam membuka paket benar-benar luar biasa, saya mendapatkan Kylian Mbappe TOTY 117 TIGA KALI, mendapatkan Lamine Yamal 116, dan mengamankan Paolo Maldini 117 dan Edwin Van Der Sar 117 yang baru!

Saksikan saat saya menyelesaikan Lencana TOTY, menukar pemain duplikat dengan Token Fase 2, dan akhirnya membuka Cafu yang legendaris untuk melengkapi pertahanan impian saya. Kami juga membawa skuad 125 OVR baru ke Head to Head untuk uji coba gameplay!
